All right.

00:13:34.272 --> 00:13:35.482 position:50% align:center
[KEI'S MOTHER]
Hm?

00:13:48.161 --> 00:13:51.998 position:50% align:center
Oh, man, I'm so embarrassed.

00:14:04.594 --> 00:14:07.180 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT 3D] That book is
really moving, isn't it?

00:14:07.263 --> 00:14:08.682 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
It is.

00:14:08.765 --> 00:14:11.810 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT 3E] Hey, Tomono,
do you prefer to read or write?

00:14:11.893 --> 00:14:15.063 position:50% align:center
Well, um, I do think
I'd like to try writing.

00:14:15.146 --> 00:14:18.400 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT 3E] Ah! There's the
literature club recruiter!

00:14:18.483 --> 00:14:20.318 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
What are you planning to do?

00:14:20.402 --> 00:14:21.528 position:50% align:center
I knew from the beginning

00:14:21.611 --> 00:14:24.155 position:50% align:center
that I wanted to join
the literature club.

00:14:24.239 --> 00:14:27.742 position:50% align:center
[KEI] Hm. I need some more
time to think about it.

00:14:33.039 --> 00:14:34.332 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Akebi?

00:14:35.583 --> 00:14:37.752 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI gasps]
You've already decided

00:14:37.836 --> 00:14:39.629 position:50% align:center
which club you're joining?

00:14:39.713 --> 00:14:41.089 position:50% align:center
I envy you.

00:14:41.172 --> 00:14:43.842 position:50% align:center
I keep waffling back and
forth between them all.

00:14:43.925 --> 00:14:46.469 position:50% align:center
Maybe I should just join
the literature club, too.

00:14:46.553 --> 00:14:48.638 position:50% align:center
No, you shouldn't
decide that way!

00:14:48.722 --> 00:14:51.474 position:50% align:center
If you really have that
many things you wanna do,

00:14:51.558 --> 00:14:53.351 position:50% align:center
then you wanna make sure
and pick the right one.

00:14:53.435 --> 00:14:55.645 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Yeah, I guess.

00:14:55.729 --> 00:14:58.064 position:50% align:center
You should get a good look
at all of them first.

00:14:58.148 --> 00:15:00.483 position:50% align:center
I'll go with you.

00:15:00.567 --> 00:15:01.693 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Thanks!

00:15:26.009 --> 00:15:27.344 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
I never realized a school

00:15:27.427 --> 00:15:29.346 position:50% align:center
could have this many clubs.

00:15:29.429 --> 00:15:32.974 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] Yeah, I couldn't
believe it, either.

00:15:33.058 --> 00:15:35.018 position:50% align:center
So much for deciding,
since that just showed me

00:15:35.101 --> 00:15:37.395 position:50% align:center
even more things I want to try!

00:15:39.272 --> 00:15:45.070 position:50% align:center
Ah! Well, I'm sorry
I wasn't much help.

00:15:45.153 --> 00:15:48.073 position:50% align:center
What? Why do you say that?
I had so much fun!

00:15:51.117 --> 00:15:52.285 position:50% align:center
I guess I just need to go home

00:15:52.369 --> 00:15:54.371 position:50% align:center
and try my best to really
think it through.

00:15:54.454 --> 00:15:56.831 position:50% align:center
Thanks so much for
doing this with me!

00:16:00.877 --> 00:16:02.712 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:16:02.796 --> 00:16:06.466 position:50% align:center
I seriously hope you find a club
that's just perfect for you.

00:16:20.438 --> 00:16:24.067 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO, KOMICHI panting]

00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:26.778 position:50% align:center
Sure is coming down.

00:16:26.861 --> 00:16:29.114 position:50% align:center
Oh, my gosh, you're
soaked, Kojou.

00:16:29.197 --> 00:16:30.949 position:50% align:center
--[TOMONO] Huh?
--I'm so sorry.

00:16:31.032 --> 00:16:32.575 position:50% align:center
If you hadn't been
visiting clubs with me...

00:16:32.659 --> 00:16:34.994 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] Mm-mm. I'm more
worried about you.

00:16:35.078 --> 00:16:37.247 position:50% align:center
Aren't you cold
in those thin clothes?

00:16:37.330 --> 00:16:38.498 position:50% align:center
Nah. I'm--

00:16:38.581 --> 00:16:39.582 position:50% align:center
[sneezes]

00:16:39.666 --> 00:16:40.583 position:50% align:center
You see?

00:16:40.667 --> 00:16:42.544 position:50% align:center
Take those wet things off.

00:17:03.314 --> 00:17:05.734 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
This is a little embarrassing.

00:17:25.754 --> 00:17:27.464 position:50% align:center
It's so warm.

00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.299 position:50% align:center
Thank you so much!

00:17:30.300 --> 00:17:34.054 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO giggles] You look a
little more grown-up in that.

00:17:34.137 --> 00:17:35.597 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:17:38.141 --> 00:17:39.768 position:50% align:center
Oh! That's just--

00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:43.188 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] It's the novel
I'm going to read from

00:17:43.271 --> 00:17:44.689 position:50% align:center
at the club's next meeting.

00:17:44.773 --> 00:17:48.109 position:50% align:center
You're doing a reading, huh?
That sounds fun!

00:17:48.193 --> 00:17:51.154 position:50% align:center
Hardly. It'll be my first time.

00:17:51.237 --> 00:17:53.823 position:50% align:center
I can't read in front
of other people.

00:17:53.907 --> 00:17:56.368 position:50% align:center
C'mon, you're gonna be great!

00:17:56.451 --> 00:17:58.453 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Have you ever done it before?

00:17:58.536 --> 00:18:03.208 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] Mm-hm. Although, it
was only for my little sister.

00:18:03.291 --> 00:18:05.126 position:50% align:center
You know what my
favorite thing is?

00:18:05.210 --> 00:18:08.004 position:50% align:center
The back of Kao's head while
she looks at the book.

00:18:12.133 --> 00:18:14.719 position:50% align:center
I'd like to hear it, too.

00:18:14.803 --> 00:18:16.638 position:50% align:center
The way your sister does.

00:18:19.808 --> 00:18:21.101 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Sure!

00:18:31.319 --> 00:18:34.781 position:50% align:center
You may have to help me.
Kanji's difficult.

00:18:40.537 --> 00:18:44.708 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] <i>Beyond the Blue Sky</i>
by Imai Tsutomu.

00:18:44.791 --> 00:18:47.877 position:50% align:center
"With five minutes until
the bell, I rush to hurriedly

00:18:47.961 --> 00:18:51.381 position:50% align:center
clear everything off
the top of my desk.

00:18:51.464 --> 00:18:54.134 position:50% align:center
It's been six months
since the accident.

00:18:54.217 --> 00:18:57.470 position:50% align:center
And suddenly, as I hobble
along on my crutches,

00:18:57.554 --> 00:19:00.306 position:50% align:center
a large spider," uh...

00:19:00.390 --> 00:19:02.017 position:50% align:center
Mm...

00:19:04.978 --> 00:19:07.564 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] "A large spider
languidly passes me by

00:19:07.647 --> 00:19:10.066 position:50% align:center
on the walk.

00:19:10.150 --> 00:19:12.027 position:50% align:center
I look up at the sky."

00:19:17.115 --> 00:19:19.993 position:50% align:center
[sighs] "So free.

00:19:20.076 --> 00:19:22.579 position:50% align:center
How lucky the clouds are."

00:19:24.456 --> 00:19:25.832 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
"Tomorrow is the final round

00:19:25.915 --> 00:19:28.293 position:50% align:center
of the prefectural tournament.

00:19:28.376 --> 00:19:30.962 position:50% align:center
And I was supposed
to be in it, too.

00:19:31.046 --> 00:19:35.675 position:50% align:center
'Hey!' A voice that sounds much
too deep to be a middle schooler

00:19:35.759 --> 00:19:38.887 position:50% align:center
calls out to me
from behind." Right.

00:19:38.970 --> 00:19:41.598 position:50% align:center
[clears throat] "Hey!"

00:19:43.016 --> 00:19:46.770 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO laughs]

00:19:46.853 --> 00:19:48.563 position:50% align:center
[BOTH laugh]

00:19:52.901 --> 00:19:55.487 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] "Slow, relaxed
footsteps approach me,

00:19:55.570 --> 00:19:58.239 position:50% align:center
resounding quietly.

00:19:58.323 --> 00:20:02.243 position:50% align:center
Then, suddenly, someone enters
my field of vision.

00:20:02.327 --> 00:20:04.913 position:50% align:center
'I know of a club that's
perfect for you!'"

00:20:33.441 --> 00:20:36.236 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:36.319 --> 00:20:37.696 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:40.365 --> 00:20:42.242 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Hey, Mom?

00:20:45.578 --> 00:20:47.580 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:20:47.664 --> 00:20:49.958 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Uh, sorry 'bout that.

00:20:53.461 --> 00:20:55.922 position:50% align:center
But look, it stopped raining.

00:21:00.677 --> 00:21:04.180 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] I am so sorry!
I must have been heavy.

00:21:04.264 --> 00:21:07.142 position:50% align:center
Not at all! That
actually made me happy!

00:21:07.225 --> 00:21:09.436 position:50% align:center
My sister's always going on
about how my mom's lap

00:21:09.519 --> 00:21:10.937 position:50% align:center
is comfier than mine.

00:21:11.021 --> 00:21:13.440 position:50% align:center
Totally drives me up the wall!

00:21:13.523 --> 00:21:15.900 position:50% align:center
So, how did my lap
feel? Be honest!

00:21:15.984 --> 00:21:20.071 position:50% align:center
Oh. Yeah, it--
it felt really nice.

00:21:20.155 --> 00:21:23.324 position:50% align:center
Also, you read well.

00:21:23.408 --> 00:21:24.868 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Huh?

00:21:24.951 --> 00:21:27.746 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] Akebi, why don't we
take a look at one last club?

00:21:27.829 --> 00:21:29.164 position:50% align:center
That sound okay?

00:21:33.168 --> 00:21:34.961 position:50% align:center
[CLASS]
Good morning.

00:21:35.045 --> 00:21:36.212 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Morning!

00:21:36.296 --> 00:21:37.547 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Morning.

00:21:37.630 --> 00:21:39.716 position:50% align:center
Akebi, come on,
it's not too late!

00:21:39.799 --> 00:21:41.217 position:50% align:center
You should join the
softball club with me,

00:21:41.301 --> 00:21:43.678 position:50% align:center
and we'll aim for the nationals!

00:21:43.762 --> 00:21:46.139 position:50% align:center
Roubai lets students
join multiple clubs.

00:21:46.222 --> 00:21:47.640 position:50% align:center
So? Wanna climb?

00:21:47.724 --> 00:21:50.310 position:50% align:center
Both of those do sound like
fun, but I think I might've

00:21:50.393 --> 00:21:52.395 position:50% align:center
finally found the club
that's right for me.

00:21:52.479 --> 00:21:55.315 position:50% align:center
--[ERIKA] Oh, I see.
--[TOUKO] Really? What is it?

00:21:55.398 --> 00:21:56.316 position:50% align:center
Hi.

00:21:56.399 --> 00:21:58.276 position:50% align:center
Oh, good morning, Tanigawa!

00:21:58.360 --> 00:21:59.527 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA, TOUKO]
Morning!

00:21:59.611 --> 00:22:01.613 position:50% align:center
I think I've settled on
the club I'm joining.

00:22:01.696 --> 00:22:03.073 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Huh?

00:22:03.156 --> 00:22:04.741 position:50% align:center
It's Photography.

00:22:06.368 --> 00:22:08.036 position:50% align:center
Of course, that's
perfect for you!

00:22:08.119 --> 00:22:09.162 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Well?

00:22:09.245 --> 00:22:10.622 position:50% align:center
What did you finally
decide on, Akebi?

00:22:10.705 --> 00:22:13.041 position:50% align:center
Come on, you have to tell us!

00:22:14.250 --> 00:22:15.543 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO chuckles]

00:22:19.255 --> 00:22:20.965 position:50% align:center
Drama club for me!